init_text: Your entire life, you've been told you're deathly allergic to bees. You've always had people protecting you from them, be it your mother or a hired hand. Today, one slips through and lands on your shoulder. You hear a tiny voice say "Your Majesty, what are your orders?"

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You look around and see that you are surrounded by tiny bees, all of them bowing to you.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: A tiny bee flies up to your face and says "Your Majesty, you must tell us what to do."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You realize that you are in a dream, and that you can control it.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You decide to try to wake yourself up.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You look at your body, you are a bee, you are a bee, you are a bee.
